@host = https://localhost:7150

### Log in — returns an access token in the body, sets the refresh_token HttpOnly cookie
# @name login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "admin", "password": "password" }

### Call a protected endpoint with the access token
GET {{host}}/secure
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Admin-only endpoint (200 for admin, 403 for a User-role token)
GET {{host}}/secure/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Refresh — sends the cookie automatically, rotates the refresh token, returns a new access token
POST {{host}}/auth/refresh

### Log out — revokes the refresh token and clears the cookie
POST {{host}}/auth/logout

### No token → 401
GET {{host}}/secure
